+    """Fused RMSNorm + router GEMV for DeepSeek V4.
+
+    Returns ``(normed_x, router_logits)`` where
+        normed_x[m,k]      = x[m,k] * rsqrt(mean(x[m]^2) + eps) * norm_weight[k]
+        router_logits[m,n] = sum_k(normed_x[m,k] * gate_weight[n,k])
